---
---

<section class="section testi-section">
  <div class="section-label">// What brands say</div>
  <h2>THEY STOPPED<br />OVERTHINKING CONTENT.</h2>
  <div class="testimonials fade-in">
    <div class="testi-card">
      <div class="testi-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
      <p class="testi-quote">"We had no idea our reviews were this funny. MemeMyReviews turned our Amazon reviews into our best-performing Instagram content. It runs itself."</p>
      <div class="testi-author">
        <div class="testi-avatar" style="background:#c084fc;">K</div>
        <div>
          <div class="testi-name">Katie R.</div>
          <div class="testi-role">Founder, Barkwell Pet Co.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="testi-card">
      <div class="testi-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
      <p class="testi-quote">"I replaced my entire social media manager's weekly deliverable with this tool. The newsletter alone is worth 10x what I'm paying."</p>
      <div class="testi-author">
        <div class="testi-avatar" style="background:#f97316;">M</div>
        <div>
          <div class="testi-name">Marcus T.</div>
          <div class="testi-role">DTC Brand, 7-fig revenue</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="testi-card">
      <div class="testi-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
      <p class="testi-quote">"The memes are actually good. Not just slapped text on a stock photo — real trending formats with our reviews baked in. Clients love it."</p>
      <div class="testi-author">
        <div class="testi-avatar" style="background:#22c55e;">R</div>
        <div>
          <div class="testi-name">Rachel S.</div>
          <div class="testi-role">Social Media Agency Owner</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testi-section {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testi-section {
      padding: 80px 48px;
    }
  }

  .testimonials {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 64px;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .testimonials {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .testi-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 24px;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testi-card {
      padding: 28px;
    }
  }

  .testi-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .testi-stars {
    color: #fbbf24;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .testi-quote {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testi-quote {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }

  .testi-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .testi-avatar {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--cream);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .testi-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .testi-role {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
  }
</style>
